+ If there are any new tests, make sure the data to run the test is included in the data bundle
    Add files to rapidtide/rapidtide/data/examples/databundle if needed
    Change the "bundledata" script accordingly
    Run the bundledata script

+ Edit CHANGELOG.md (use git log to get the history)

+ Sync everything to GitHub

+ Refresh local installation

+ Create a new release
    git tag -a vX.Y.Z -m "vX.Y.Z"
    git push origin vX.Y.Z
    
+ Edit new tag on GitHub

+ Check the DockerHub and PyPi deployment Actions
